"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The code sets the x-ticks and x-tick labels to unique dates before setting the major locator and formatter for the x-axis. This can lead to inconsistencies in the x-axis ticks and labels. The x-ticks and labels should be set after configuring the major locator and formatter.\",\n  \"patch\": \"16a17\\n> ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(MonthLocator())\\n> ax.xaxis.set_major_formatter(DateFormatter('%Y-%m'))\\n17,18d17\\n< ax.set_xticks(df.date.unique())\\n< ax.set_xticklabels(labels=df.date.unique(), rotation=45)\\n20a20\\n> ax.set_xticks(df.date.unique())\\n> ax.set_xticklabels(labels=df.date.unique(), rotation=45)\\n\"\n}"